WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Triom' is a game featuring a number of trios of shapes that are
all linked together and the goal is to place those shapes in such
a way that each trio has the same shapes.

  There are two ways to move a shape: Swap 2 shapes in a trio or
move the linked shapes from one trio to another.

  Try to complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

